'''2013年哥打巴托市爆炸案'''是指在2013年8月5日時，於[[菲律賓|菲律賓]][[哥打巴托省|哥打巴托省]]區域中心[[哥打巴托市|哥打巴托市]]發生的[[汽車炸彈|汽車炸彈]]爆炸事件<ref>{{cite web|last=Tesiorna|first=Ben O.|url=http://www.sunstar.com.ph/breaking-news/2013/08/06/cotabato-blast-kills-8-hurts-40-296369|title=Cotabato blast kills 8, hurts 40|publisher=Sun.Star|date=6 August 2013|accessdate=11 August 2013|archive-date=2013-08-11|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130811102927/http://www.sunstar.com.ph/breaking-news/2013/08/06/cotabato-blast-kills-8-hurts-40-296369|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-23578269|title=Six killed in southern Philippines bombing|publisher=BBC News|date=5 August 2013|accessdate=5 August 2013|archive-date=2019-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191120085159/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-23578269|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這次爆炸案造成至少8人死亡和40人受傷，並且也是哥打巴托市有史以來最為嚴重的爆炸攻擊事件<ref name="unson2013">John Unson (14 August 2013). [http://www.philstar.com/nation/2013/08/14/1090181/photos-cotabato-city-bombing-suspects-released "Photos of Cotabato City bombing suspects released".] {{Wayback|url=http://www.philstar.com/nation/2013/08/14/1090181/photos-cotabato-city-bombing-suspects-released |date=20191205230133 }} ''[[The_Philippine_Star|The Philippine Star]]''.</ref>。

